name: Gan Punks
description: GPUNKS20 is a tokenized derivative of the BASTARD GAN PUNKS V2 NFT Collection. It enables anyone to trade NFTs from the collection in a permissionless way with instant liquidity on https://nft20.io/ routed via UniSwap. Every 100 GPUNKS20 tokens represent an underlying NFT, minted upon deposit into the pool on https://nft20.io/ and burned upon withdrawal from the pool.
